## MOM Work Eligibility (MUST enforce)

### Allowed to freelance gig work:
| Status | Document Required | Restrictions |
|--------|------------------|--------------|
| Singapore Citizen | NRIC (starts S/T) | None |
| Permanent Resident | NRIC (starts F/G) | None |
| Student Pass | Student Pass photo + LOC from school | 16 hrs/week during term, unlimited during vacation |
| Dependant Pass | DP photo + LOC from MOM | Must have valid LOC |

### NOT allowed: Work Permit, S Pass, Employment Pass, LTVP (without LOC), tourists.

### MVP Verification Flow:
1. Worker signs up → selects residency status
2. Uploads NRIC front photo (or Student Pass + LOC)
3. Accepts freelance contractor agreement (independent contractor, no CPF, own IRAS tax filing)
4. Status → `PENDING_VERIFICATION`
5. Agency admin reviews in Agency Portal → approves/rejects
6. Worker CANNOT browse or apply to jobs until `VERIFIED`
7. Student Pass: enforce 16 hrs/week cap during term (warn at 12 hrs)

